text: Brachynarthron aeneipennis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1956. It is known from Ghana.BioLib.cz - Brachynarthron aeneipennis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1956
